Got me some good headshots.

1102
01:21:33,760 --> 01:21:35,603
I see.

1103
01:21:35,840 --> 01:21:37,808
What's his name?

1104
01:21:38,280 --> 01:21:40,044
Bill Thompson.

1105
01:21:40,240 --> 01:21:42,049
He's with Thompson and Gould...

1106
01:21:42,240 --> 01:21:44,527
