download the file?

1119
01:22:29,280 --> 01:22:31,009
Yes.

1120
01:22:32,160 --> 01:22:33,605
Good.

1121
01:22:34,480 --> 01:22:36,244
Okay.

1122
01:22:37,920 --> 01:22:39,809
I'll talk to you later. I love you.

1123
01:22:40,000 --> 01:22:42,571
- Bye.
- Bye.

